A well-balanced real-life drama on what happened before the first huge expos√© of the Catholic Church's major scandal, this is a must watch for fellow Catholics around the globe. It is amazing how the Boston reporters managed to prepare their report under wrap of secrecy in 2001, and maintained their focus even when the need to report on the 9/11 attack nearly eclipsed the significance of their reporting.

And before you try to dismiss this film as anti-Catholic, L'Osservatore Romano (the official Vatican newspaper) has officially endorsed this film as factual and not an anti-Catholic one as many had feared. So please, watch it.
