Greatly deserving of the Academy's "Best Picture" award Spotlight delivers a intelligent punch to the gut full of cold hard facts overlooked by the American people that will leave you out of breath. The suspenseful investigation led by the Boston Globe's Spotlight special investigations team keeps delving deeper and deeper into a gaping hole in justice. Every time you think you have grasped the gravity of the situation the protagonists find themselves in, you're quickly proven wrong even up until the final scene if the film and the roll of the credits. This film shows a depressing story, the importance of accountability and gives new meaning to the phrase "look the other way." Featuring an All-Star cast filled with performances from Liev Schreiber, Mark Ruffalo, Michael Keaton, Rachel McAdams, and Stanley Tucci your eyes will be glued to the screen for this wild ride.
