Imagine there is a house with 10 rooms. In 9 of the rooms they feed the hungry, educate the uneducated, heal the sick, save souls. BUT In the one remaining they force innocent children to perform perverse sexual acts, crush souls and obstruct justice.  Do you burn down the house?  This is a serious question. DO YOU BURN DOWN THE HOUSE?!  Do you throw open the door and shed light on the diabolical culture that has existed for a period of time only God can quantify?  
