This is one of my top 3 favorites of 2015. Tom McCarthy delivers a perfectly executed account of The Boston Globe's Spotlight team's investigation into child sex abuse in the Catholic church complete with near-perfect acting, excellent pacing, and a beautifully simple score. This movie has it all.
