With no surprises or big reveals, Spotlght chugs along crossing all the Ts and making us feel like we're part of the exploration. An impeccable cast with tone perfect writing and acting...this is a "must see" this year and while it might not be able to overtake the favorites for Oscar...it's a very solid movie and an important look into the value of a working paper for investigative journalism.
