Methodical, precise and to the point. Just like the investigative journalism it portrays. The Hulk, Batman and Sabretooth et al are working together to uncover disgusting story of sexual abuse in the Catholic church. The way they do it reminds us why we need good, tough journalists, the ones who are absolutely devoted to serving the general public even if that requires severe personal sacrifices. It's genuinely fascinating to see how a ground-breaking news story comes together.
