Magnificent!!! But I don't recommend this movie to everyone. I would say..."Spotlight" is the 2010s' answer to the 1970s' "All The President's Men." If you didn't like ATPM, you might not like Spotlight. They have many of the same characteristics: intricate plot, succinct dialogue, and deliberate pacing. But if you loved movies like "The Insider (1999)" and the aforementioned "All the President's Men (1976)," Spotlight might be right up your alley. Along with "Ex Machina," "Sicario," and "Steve Jobs," Spotlight is (I think) one of this year's best movies.
