Spotlight

Based on the true story of how the Spotlight journalists working for the Boston Globe uncovered the scandalous child molestation cover-up by the local Catholic Archdiocese.

A star-studded cast drives this hard hitting drama about a very difficult subject where the corruption of keeping the Catholic Church's horrible secret in the dark branches out much farther than the religion itself. 

